# Production build flag config — ADR-016 (Ops cutover, 2026-07-10): COEXIST.
# The Ops redesign (/ops/*) ships ON as a browse/monitoring layer ALONGSIDE the
# legacy screens (legacy retained for all editing + the ImportView operator tabs).
# TD-27: VITE_OPS_REDESIGN is a BUILD-TIME flag — rollback = redeploy a build with
# this false/absent. Staged rollout (staging → canary → prod) is a deploy-pipeline
# concern; see docs/runbooks/ops-shell.md §rollout. Dev (.env, gitignored) stays OFF.
VITE_OPS_REDESIGN=true
